prod.desciption:
The Air Jordan 1 Light Fusion Red features a white leather upper with Light Fusion Red overlays and Laser Orange on the Swoosh and ankle wrap. A woven Nike label stitched atop the tongue completes the design.

The Air Jordan 1 Light Fusion Red released in June of 2021 and retailed for $170.
